00:00:06.465 --> 00:00:09.630
You have to update the IP address or

00:00:09.630 --> 00:00:13.605
the name servers of the web server to the domain name.

00:00:13.605 --> 00:00:17.325
Let us first understand why it is important.

00:00:17.325 --> 00:00:22.870
Whenever a user types the URL in the address bar of a web browser,

00:00:22.870 --> 00:00:27.260
browser knocks the door of the domain, not knock.

00:00:27.260 --> 00:00:34.190
Domain provides the IP address of the web server where the data of the website is stored.

00:00:34.190 --> 00:00:40.370
