00:00:43.400 --> 00:00:48.155
the IP address of the web server where the data of the website is saved,

00:00:48.155 --> 00:00:53.015
then a web browser will not be able to pressing the web content to the user,

00:00:53.015 --> 00:00:55.910
and the result will be an error page.

00:00:55.910 --> 00:00:58.715
The IP address or name server.

00:00:58.715 --> 00:01:05.165
